Class TextPartiallyRawComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.hadoop.io.TextPartiallyRawComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PartiallyRawComparator<Text>, org.apache.ignite.internal.processors.hadoop.io.PartiallyOffheapRawComparatorEx<Text>

    public class TextPartiallyRawComparator
extends Object
implements PartiallyRawComparator<Text>, org.apache.ignite.internal.processors.hadoop.io.PartiallyOffheapRawComparatorEx<Text>
    Partial raw comparator for Text data type.

    Implementation is borrowed from org.apache.hadoop.io.FastByteComparisons and adopted to Ignite infrastructure.
